node.text: Jordan spent the weekend with the five babes while mom was out of town. slow clap for not only taking them all to the zoo but also doing all the hair + remembering the hair bows! you’re the best @masseyjordan.

node.title: Dad’s Weekend Solo with FIVE KIDS!

node.text: 2 years in the making, and finally we have shared our very first YouTube video! Christmas Gift Guide 2019 with some of our favorites! you guysssss I can’t believe it🙈 show us some love!

node.text: it’s been a minute since I’ve shared the bunk room! we have done a lot to this house to make it a home in the last year- by far the best transformation was the media room reno to create this space for the boys! swipe for the before! last thing.. too early for Halloween jams? asking for a friend👻

node.text: happy anniversary, @masseyjordan❤️ twenty years ago you took a 15 year old Amber to get her belly button pierced. eighteen years ago you prayed with a 16 year old Amber at church camp to accept Jesus Christ into her heart. sixteen years ago you married a 20 year old Amber and made all her dreams come true❤️ ten years ago we battled and won against infertility.. and all these years later, here we are- a lifetime of memories and a very full house. super thankful for this life, my love.
